      <title>日本基金青睐德国债券，避开法国债券</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-11/japanese-funds-embrace-german-bonds-while-shunning-french-debt</link>
      <description><![CDATA[9 月份，日本投资者购买了自 2018 年以来最大数量的德国主权债务，同时出于对法国财政状况的担忧，日本投资者继续撤出法国债券。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-11/japanese-funds-embrace-german-bonds-while-shunning-french-debt</guid>
